                            <comment id="17732684" author="tilman" created="Wed, 14 Jun 2023 18:27:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause is &lt;tt&gt;processSoftMask&lt;/tt&gt;, it doesn&apos;t save and restore textMatrix while the softmask is processed. The softmask has text and when encountering the &quot;ET&quot; operator, the textMatrix is reset to null. In &lt;tt&gt;processType3Stream()&lt;/tt&gt; we avoid this problem by saving the textMatrix and another variable. It&apos;s really surprising that this hasn&apos;t hit us all these years.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17732837" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 15 Jun 2023 03:52:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1910413 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1910413&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1910413&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5621&quot; title=&quot;NullPointerException in PDFStreamEngine.showText&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5621&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5621&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: avoid NPE if the softmask has text&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17732838" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 15 Jun 2023 03:52:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1910414 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1910414&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1910414&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5621&quot; title=&quot;NullPointerException in PDFStreamEngine.showText&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5621&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5621&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: avoid NPE if the softmask has text&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17732841" author="tilman" created="Thu, 15 Jun 2023 04:25:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in snapshot, should appear there soon:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.29-SNAPSHOT/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.29-SNAPSHOT/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

